\"to\": 1325}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There are far too many genuine things for us to be angry about, and to take steps to address, without manufactured outrage about something at the Olympics which, [as pointed out by another person's post], did not really happen anyway.\", \"from\": 1360, \"to\": 1595, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"far too many genuine things\", \"from\": 1371, \"to\": 1398}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1403, \"to\": 1405}, {\"ngram\": \"steps\", \"from\": 1437, \"to\": 1442}, {\"ngram\": \"manufactured outrage\", \"from\": 1463, \"to\": 1483}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1490, \"to\": 1499}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1503, \"to\": 1515}, {\"ngram\": \"another person's post\", \"from\": 1542, \"to\": 1563}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We need to get our priorities right.\", \"from\": 1597, \"to\": 1634, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our priorities\", \"from\": 1613, \"to\": 1627}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"To be honest even if it had been the Last Supper painting being recreated, at the end of the day it's a painting, and probably not a an accurate depiction of the Last Supper anyway!\\\"\", \"from\": 1636, \"to\": 1819, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Last Supper painting\", \"from\": 1670, \"to\": 1694}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 1715, \"to\": 1722}, {\"ngram\": \"the day\", \"from\": 1726, \"to\": 1733}, {\"ngram\": \"a painting\", \"from\": 1739, \"to\": 1749}, {\"ngram\": \"probably not a an accurate depiction\", \"from\": 1755, \"to\": 1791}, {\"ngram\": \"the Last Supper\", \"from\": 1795, \"to\": 1810}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A number of people commented online to support Rev Hughes' comments.\", \"from\": 1821, \"to\": 1889, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1872, \"end\": 1878, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\", \"score\": 0.9999399858267091, \"rank\": 3.001678107963063e-05, \"text\": \"Hughes\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\